{"tid":1405670,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"大家係點樣知道麥記除咗有甜酸醬之外重有芥末醬同燒烤醬?","createTime":"2019-08-04T10:44:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-07T16:55:45.000Z","uid":215860,"like":13,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"8941b0038d7db453897e3863040d364581024fc1","tid":1405670,"uid":215860,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T10:44:22.000Z","msg":"麥樂雞平時除咗有甜酸醬之外，重有芥末醬同燒烤醬，相信好多人都知道。但係，其實我一直以嚟都未見過廣告有講，平時叫麥樂雞時職員又唔會問你要咩醬，自動就畀甜酸醬你，除非你主動要求要其他醬。<br />\n我好好奇，你地係點樣知道有另外呢兩隻醬呢？<br />\n我先講下自己先，我係大概小學2年班時(我今年30)我阿媽帶我食麥記同我講，我問返佢點知，佢話佢一直都知，但唔記得點樣知。<br />\n你地又係點樣知架?"},{"pid":"40ea4331ce8dd3d8999508f5697265f941d015ec","tid":1405670,"uid":165510,"like":18,"dislike":1,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T10:46:14.000Z","msg":"有左個部機揀麥樂雞個陣先知<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n85罷工！"},{"pid":"2d4e12e631bb87ad466ab7a5dd23c976ce25bc72","tid":1405670,"uid":77092,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T15:39:21.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"16a8f29660ccda6e0ee8c5f1a0bd320442535009","tid":1405670,"uid":215860,"like":11,"dislike":2,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"2d4e12e631bb87ad466ab7a5dd23c976ce25bc72","tid":1405670,"uid":77092,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T15:39:21.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T00:25:23.000Z","msg":"我問緊你地點知道有呢隻醬，唔係問你地鍾意邊隻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"382c0d400f180df09b533471774293464dbd6291","tid":1405670,"uid":108756,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"16a8f29660ccda6e0ee8c5f1a0bd320442535009","tid":1405670,"uid":215860,"like":11,"dislike":2,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"2d4e12e631bb87ad466ab7a5dd23c976ce25bc72","tid":1405670,"uid":77092,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T15:39:21.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T00:25:23.000Z","msg":"我問緊你地點知道有呢隻醬，唔係問你地鍾意邊隻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtop